info.description:
PyLinearA
=========

.. image:: https://travis-ci.org/georgy7/LinearA.svg?branch=master
:target: https://travis-ci.org/georgy7/LinearA

.. image:: https://coveralls.io/repos/github/georgy7/LinearA/badge.svg
:target: https://coveralls.io/github/georgy7/LinearA


LinearA is a new simple image format for processing, not storage: *almost raw data* in *The Linear RGBA*, the most convenient color
space for me so far. This is not a library, but a separate | app | for | pipelines.
